#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Quarkus 3.31 - Full Java 25 support, Quarkus Maven packaging, Panache Next, and more!"
msgstr "Quarkus 3.31 - フルJava 25サポート、Quarkus Mavenパッケージング、Panache Next、その他！"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "This release is packed with new features and improvements, including full Java 25 support, a new Quarkus Maven packaging type, Panache Next, Hibernate upgrades, JUnit 6 and Testcontainers 2 upgrades, and numerous enhancements to our Security extensions."
msgstr "このリリースには、フルJava 25サポート、新しいQuarkus Mavenパッケージングタイプ、Panache Next、Hibernateのアップグレード、JUnit 6とTestcontainers 2のアップグレード、およびセキュリティエクステンションへの多数の機能強化など、新機能と改善が満載されています。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "It has been two months since our last feature release, and we are excited to announce the availability of Quarkus 3.31!"
msgstr "前回の機能リリースから2ヶ月が経ち、Quarkus 3.31の提供開始を発表できることを嬉しく思います！"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Quarkus 3.31 comes with a LOT of new features and improvements:"
msgstr "Quarkus 3.31には、多くの新機能と改善が含まれています:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Full Java 25 support"
msgstr "フルJava 25サポート"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51587[#51587] - Introduce a quarkus Maven packaging and an assorted lifecycle"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51587[#51587] - Quarkus Mavenパッケージングと関連するライフサイクルの導入"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/50058[#50058] - Introduce Panache Next, our next generation of Panache with improved developer experience and new features for both Hibernate ORM and Hibernate Reactive"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/50058[#50058] - 開発者エクスペリエンスが向上し、Hibernate ORMとHibernate Reactiveの両方に新機能が追加された次世代PanacheであるPanache Nextの導入"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/50519[#50519] - Upgrade to Hibernate ORM 7.2, Reactive 3.2, Search 8.2, Elasticsearch 9.2 / OpenSearch 3.3 for clients / server (dev services)"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/50519[#50519] - Hibernate ORM 7.2、Reactive 3.2、Search 8.2、クライアント/サーバー向けElasticsearch 9.2 / OpenSearch 3.3 (dev services) へのアップグレード"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51586[#51586] - Hibernate Spatial support"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51586[#51586] - Hibernate Spatial のサポート"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51314[#51314] - Upgrade to Testcontainers 2"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51314[#51314] - Testcontainers 2 へのアップグレード"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51412[#51412] - Upgrade to JUnit 6"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51412[#51412] - JUnit 6 へのアップグレード"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/50987[#50987] - Support security annotations on Jakarta Data repositories"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/50987[#50987] - Jakarta Data リポジトリーにおけるセキュリティアノテーションのサポート"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51188[#51188] - Support `@PermissionsAllowed` security annotation on REST Data Panache endpoints"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51188[#51188] - REST Data Panache エンドポイントでの `@PermissionsAllowed` セキュリティアノテーションのサポート"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51220[#51220] - Encrypt OIDC tokens for custom TokenStateManager implementations"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51220[#51220] - カスタム TokenStateManager 実装向けのOIDCトークンの暗号化"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51383[#51383] - Allow to configure OIDC DB token state manager column sizes for tokens"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51383[#51383] - トークン向けのOIDC DBトークンステートマネージャーカラムサイズの設定を許可"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51743[#51743] - Allow to select OIDC client for individual dynamic GraphQL clients"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51743[#51743] - 個々の動的GraphQLクライアント向けOIDCクライアントの選択を許可"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51679[#51679] - Allow to assign a user and roles to a scheduled task"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51679[#51679] - スケジュールされたタスクにユーザーとロールを割り当てることを許可"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51799[#51799] - Add support for OAuth 2.0 Pushed Authorization Requests to OIDC extension"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51799[#51799] - OIDCエクステンションへのOAuth 2.0 Pushed Authorization Requestsのサポート追加"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/50603[#50603] - Enable headless AWT on Windows for native images"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/50603[#50603] - ネイティブイメージ向けWindowsでのヘッドレスAWTの有効化"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51736[#51736] - Require Maven 3.9.0+ for Quarkus projects"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51736[#51736] - QuarkusプロジェクトにはMaven 3.9.0+を要求"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51049[#51049] - Add i18n to Dev UI"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51049[#51049] - Dev UIにi18nを追加"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "As usual, this release also includes many bug fixes, including fixes for some https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51891[very old issues created in 2020], thanks to our amazing community!"
msgstr "いつものように、このリリースには、素晴らしいコミュニティーのおかげで、 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/51891[2020年に作成された非常に古い問題] の修正を含む、多くのバグ修正も含まれています！"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "We highly recommend to have a look at the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.31[migration guide] as this version comes with some important changes."
msgstr "このバージョンにはいくつかの重要な変更が含まれているため、 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.31[移行ガイド] を参照することを強くお勧めします。"

#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Update"
msgstr "Update"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "To update to Quarkus 3.31, we recommend updating to the latest version of the Quarkus CLI and run:"
msgstr "Quarkus 3.31に更新するには、Quarkus CLIの最新バージョンに更新して、以下を実行することをお勧めします:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Note that `quarkus update` can update your applications from any version of Quarkus (including 2.x) to Quarkus 3.31."
msgstr "`quarkus update` は、Quarkusの任意のバージョン（2.xを含む）からQuarkus 3.31にアプリケーションを更新できることに注意してください。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "For more information about the adjustments you need to make to your applications, please refer to the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.31[Quarkus 3.31 migration guide]."
msgstr "アプリケーションに行う必要がある調整の詳細については、 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.31[Quarkus 3.31移行ガイド] を参照してください。"

#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "What's new?"
msgstr "変更点"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Full support for Java 25"
msgstr "Java 25のフルサポート"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Quarkus 3.31 adds full support for Java 25, including Java 25 runtime images and native image builds with Mandrel."
msgstr "Quarkus 3.31は、Java 25ランタイムイメージおよびMandrelを使用したネイティブイメージビルドを含む、Java 25のフルサポートを追加します。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "If you create new projects with Java 25, the projects will fully target Java 25 by default."
msgstr "Java 25で新しいプロジェクトを作成すると、プロジェクトはデフォルトでJava 25を完全にターゲットとします。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid ""
"We were hard at work to ensure compatibility and avoid as many warnings as possible when running Quarkus applications on Java 25.\n"
"If you encounter any issues, including warnings that shouldn't be there, please report them on our https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues[bug tracker]."
msgstr "Java 25でQuarkusアプリケーションを実行する際の互換性を確保し、可能な限り多くの警告を回避するために懸命に取り組みました。そこに表示されるべきではない警告を含む問題に遭遇した場合は、 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues[バグトラッカー] に報告してください。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "New quarkus Maven packaging and lifecycle"
msgstr "新しいQuarkus Mavenパッケージングとライフサイクル"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid ""
"A few months ago, we started working on making our builds faster (see this https://quarkus.io/blog/building-large-applications/[blog post] for all the gory details).\n"
"With Quarkus 3.31, we are introducing a new Maven packaging type called `quarkus`, designed to provide a more integrated and significantly more efficient build lifecycle."
msgstr "数ヶ月前、私たちはビルドを高速化することに取り組み始めました（詳細については、この link:https://quarkus.io/blog/building-large-applications/[ブログ記事] を参照してください）。Quarkus 3.31では、より統合され、大幅に効率的なビルドライフサイクルを提供するように設計された、 `quarkus` と呼ばれる新しいMavenパッケージングタイプを導入しています。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "In other words, we move away from the default Maven `jar` lifecycle and introduce a Quarkus-specific lifecycle optimized for Quarkus applications, avoiding the execution of goals that are unnecessary in most cases."
msgstr "言い換えれば、私たちはデフォルトのMaven `jar` ライフサイクルから離れ、Quarkusアプリケーションに最適化されたQuarkus固有のライフサイクルを導入し、ほとんどの場合に不要なゴールの実行を回避します。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "It is the default for newly created Quarkus projects and it can also be used for existing projects (see the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.31#new-quarkus-packaging-and-maven-lifecycle[migration guide] for more details)."
msgstr "これは新しく作成されるQuarkusプロジェクトのデフォルトであり、既存のプロジェクトでも使用できます（詳細については、 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.31#new-quarkus-packaging-and-maven-lifecycle[移行ガイド] を参照してください）。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Larger applications"
msgstr "大規模なアプリケーション"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid ""
"This \"faster builds\" effort is particularly beneficial for larger applications and we alleviated one of the latest bottleneck for creating VERY large applications:\n"
"the number of CDI beans in the application could hit some class file limits during the build."
msgstr "この「高速ビルド」の取り組みは、大規模なアプリケーションにとって特に有益であり、非常に大規模なアプリケーションを作成する際の最新のボトルネックの1つを軽減しました。それは、アプリケーション内のCDI Beanの数がビルド中にクラスファイルの制限に達する可能性があったことです。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "With Quarkus 3.31, you shouldn't be limited by the number of CDI beans anymore."
msgstr "Quarkus 3.31では、CDI Beanの数によって制限されることはもうありません。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Panache Next"
msgstr "Panache Next"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "If you use Hibernate ORM with Quarkus, you are probably already familiar with Hibernate ORM with Panache."
msgstr "QuarkusでHibernate ORMを使用している場合、おそらくHibernate ORM with Panacheについてはすでにご存知でしょう。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid ""
"Panache Next is our next generation of Panache that brings a better developer experience and new features.\n"
"While relying on the same underlying concepts as the current Panache implementation, Panache Next introduces a more intuitive API, improved type safety, and enhanced query capabilities.\n"
"It also unifies the programming model between Hibernate ORM and Hibernate Reactive, stateful and stateless sessions, making it easier for developers to switch between them.\n"
"Finally, it integrates seamlessly with Jakarta Data."
msgstr "Panache Nextは、より良い開発者エクスペリエンスと新機能をもたらす次世代のPanacheです。現在のPanache実装と同じ基盤となる概念に依拠しつつ、Panache Nextはより直感的なAPI、改善された型安全性、および強化されたクエリ機能を提供します。また、Hibernate ORMとHibernate Reactive、ステートフルおよびステートレスセッション間のプログラミングモデルを統一し、開発者がそれらを簡単に切り替えられるようにします。最後に、Jakarta Dataとシームレスに統合されます。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "There would be a lot more to say but the best is to have a look at the https://quarkus.io/guides/hibernate-panache-next[documentation], and give it a try."
msgstr "さらに多くのことを言うべきですが、最善は link:https://quarkus.io/guides/hibernate-panache-next[ドキュメント] を見て試してみることです。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "It is still experimental and we are very looking forward to your feedback."
msgstr "これはまだ実験的な段階であり、皆様からのフィードバックをお待ちしております。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Hibernate"
msgstr "Hibernate ORM"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Quarkus 3.31 upgrades Hibernate ORM to 7.2, Hibernate Reactive to 3.2, Hibernate Search to 8.2, and the Elasticsearch/OpenSearch clients and servers to 9.2/3.3 respectively."
msgstr "Quarkus 3.31は、Hibernate ORMを7.2、Hibernate Reactiveを3.2、Hibernate Searchを8.2、Elasticsearch/OpenSearchクライアントおよびサーバーをそれぞれ9.2/3.3にアップグレードします。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "It also brings support for Hibernate Spatial, allowing developers to work with spatial data types and perform spatial queries in their Quarkus applications."
msgstr "また、Hibernate Spatialのサポートも導入され、開発者はQuarkusアプリケーションで空間データ型を操作し、空間クエリを実行できるようになります。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "JUnit 6 and Testcontainers 2"
msgstr "JUnit 6とTestcontainers 2"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "We upgraded to JUnit 6 (the update is relatively straightforward) and Testcontainers 2 (which comes with a lot more breaking changes)."
msgstr "JUnit 6（更新は比較的簡単）とTestcontainers 2（より多くの破壊的変更を伴う）にアップグレードしました。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid ""
"The `-junit5` extensions have been renamed to `-junit`, with relocations in place to avoid breaking existing projects.\n"
"Use `quarkus update` to get them updated automatically."
msgstr "`quarkus-junit5` エクステンションは `-junit` に名前が変更されました。既存のプロジェクトを壊さないようにリロケーションが設定されています。 `quarkus update` を使用して自動的に更新してください。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Security"
msgstr "セキュリティー"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "What would be a Quarkus release without security improvements?"
msgstr "セキュリティの改善なしにQuarkusリリースがあるでしょうか？"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "This release comes with a lot of improvements to our security extensions, including:"
msgstr "このリリースには、当社のセキュリティエクステンションに対する多くの改善が含まれており、以下を含みます:"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Maven 3.9 required"
msgstr "Maven 3.9が必須"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Maven 3.9 is now required to build Quarkus applications."
msgstr "Quarkusアプリケーションをビルドするには、Maven 3.9が必須になりました。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Headless AWT on Windows for native images"
msgstr "ネイティブイメージでのWindowsにおけるヘッドレスAWT"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "We added support for headless AWT on Windows for native images to our AWT extension."
msgstr "AWTエクステンションに、ネイティブイメージでのWindowsにおけるヘッドレスAWTのサポートを追加しました。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "I18N for Dev UI"
msgstr "Dev UIのI18N"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "The Dev UI is now internationalized."
msgstr "Dev UIが国際化されました。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Contributions are welcome to improve the translations and add new languages."
msgstr "翻訳の改善や新しい言語の追加への貢献を歓迎します。"

#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Full changelog"
msgstr "完全な変更履歴"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "You can get the full changelog of https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.31.0.CR1[3.31.0.CR1], https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.31.0[3.31.0], and https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.31.1[3.31.1] on GitHub."
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.31.0.CR1[3.31.0.CR1] 、 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.31.0[3.31.0] 、および link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.31.1[3.31.1] の完全な変更履歴はGitHubで確認できます。"

#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2026-01-28-quarkus-3-31-released.adoc
msgid "Contributors"
msgstr "コントリビューター"

#. type: Plain text
